==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Progressionist
<hw>Pro*gres"sion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who holds to a belief in the progression of
society toward perfection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who maintains the doctrine of progression in
organic forms; -- opposed to <contr>uniformitarian</contr>.</def>
<rj><au>H. Spencer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Progressist</ent>⟦br⟧
